 Gelb </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="gallery-row" style="width: 640px; height: 213px;" data-original-width="640" data-original-height="213" > <div class="gallery-group" style="width: 213px; height: 213px;" data-original-width="213" data-original-height="213" > <div class="tiled-gallery-item " itemprop="associatedMedia" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject"> <a href="https://blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/2021/01/20/advice-for-applying-to-reu-programs-from-recent-participants/minino/" border="0" itemprop="url"> <meta itemprop="width" content="209"> <meta itemprop="height" content="209"> <img data-attachment-id="1814" data-orig-file="https://blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Minino.png" data-orig-size="600,800" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Minino" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Minino.png?fit=225%2C300&#038;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Minino.png?fit=600%2C800&#038;ssl=1" src="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Minino.png?w=209&#038;h=209&#038;crop=1&#038;ssl=1" width="209" height="209" data-original-width="209" data-original-height="209" itemprop="http://schema.org/image" title="Minino" alt="Amaury Miniño" style="width: 209px; height: 209px;" /> </a> <div class="tiled-gallery-caption" itemprop="caption description"> Amaury Miniño </div> </div> </div> <div class="gallery-group" style="width: 213px; height: 213px;" data-original-width="213" da