/" border="0" itemprop="url"> <meta itemprop="width" content="209"> <meta itemprop="height" content="209"> <img data-attachment-id="1816" data-orig-file="https://blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Trent.png" data-orig-size="600,800" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Trent" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Trent.png?fit=225%2C300&#038;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Trent.png?fit=600%2C800&#038;ssl=1" src="https://i2.wp.com/blogs.ams.org/mathmentoringnetwork/files/2021/01/Trent.png?w=209&#038;h=209&#038;crop=1&#038;ssl=1" width="209" height="209" data-original-width="209" data-original-height="209" itemprop="http://schema.org/image" title="Trent" alt="Lee Trent" style="width: 209px; height: 209px;" /> </a> <div class="tiled-gallery-caption" itemprop="caption description"> Lee Trent </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>
<p>Alvaro Carbonero is an undergraduate at the University of Nevada, Las Vegas. He has participated in the REU programs at Lafayette College and Rochester Institute of Technology.<br /><br />Brittany Gelb is an undergraduate at Muhlenberg College. She has participated in the REU programs at Lafayette College and DIMACS.<br /><br />Amaury Miniño is a first-year PhD student at Colorado State University. He graduated from Florida Atlantic University and has participated in the F-LEARN program and the Mathematical Sciences Research Institute Undergraduate Program (MSRI-UP).<br /><br />Vanessa Sun is an undergraduate at Macaulay Honors College at Hunter College, City University of New York (CUNY). She participated in the Mathematical Sciences Research Institute Undergraduate Program (MSRI-UP).<br /><br />Lee Trent is pursuing her undergraduate degree at Rose-Hulman Institute of Technology. She has been a counselor at Rose-Hulman AMP and PROMYS and participated in the REU at Grand Valley State University.</p>
